rong lot and then text some sad story about skimming the invite.<\/p>\n<p>Map &#8211;\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/Q6B2W\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow nofollow\">http:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/Q6B2W<\/a>\u00a0(see, told you it was a different place than you were thinking)<\/p>\n<p>Directions<br \/>\nTake IN-46 east until you reach Yellowwood Rd (sign for Yellowwood State Forest will lead the way)<br \/>\nTurn left to follow the road in the cornfield then left again when you hit the T<br \/>\nStay on that road by baring right toward the campgrounds<br \/>\nMake the 2nd Left (the first is a residence\u2019s driveway)<br \/>\nLook for hashers, crack a beer, hash, drink, sing, GTFO<\/p>\n<p>See you all there!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>One of the plenitude of benefits that comes with being a Blooming Fool is the profuse array of shiggy adorning our nearby environs. That is why returners wax rhapsodic when they remember hashes past and yearn for the chance to &hellip; <a href=\"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/?p=1261\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1261"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=1261"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1261\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1263,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/